    Download a dataset from the API INE service

    Usage

    get_data(
  dataset,
  version = NULL,
  col_list = NULL,
  save_where = c("renviron", "disk", "both", "no_message")
)

    Arguments

    dataset

    string. The possible values are "ene", "epf_personas", "epf_gastos", "enusc" or "esi".

    version

    string by default is the newest version.

    col_list

    character vector by default is all columns. The possible values can be obtained through the get_columns function.

    save_where

    string by default is "renviron", the possible values are "renviron","disk","both","no_message".

    Value

    dataframe

    # Get dataset of "ene" survey from september-november-october 2020 quarter and selecting columns
